- Gia thn askhsh exo ftiaxei 1 thread gia ton chef kai N=7 threads gia tous customers.

- Exo ftiaxei dyo synarthseis (chef kai customer) oi opoies trexoun ta threads. 
  To thread tou chef termatizei otan exoun ejiphretithei oloi oi pelates.

- Xrhsimopoio 4 semaphores gia ton sygxronismo ton threads. 

- H main dhmiourgei 3 customer threads kai meta perimenei 3 second.
  Ara o chef exipiretei 3 pelates kai meta einai sto fb mexri
   na erthoun oi epomenoi 3 pelates, kai ta loipa.

